BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Frenzy Coffee 1st Birthday Celebration – Live DJ & Vendors
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260403T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260403T173000
UID:10000510-1775210400-1775237400@davisdowntown.com
DESCRIPTION:Help Frenzy Coffee celebrate their 1st full year in Davis! \nC
 ome join the fun at this all-day birthday party featuring live DJ sets and
  a variety of local vendors. Whether you’re grabbing your morning coffee
 \, stopping by for lunch\, or hanging out in the afternoon\, there will be
  great music\, good vibes\, and plenty of ways to celebrate with the commu
 nity. \nBring your friends\, family\, or coworkers and enjoy the lively at
 mosphere right in the heart of downtown Davis. Everyone is welcome! \nFree
  to attend – no tickets needed. Just stop by\, enjoy the music\, shop lo
 cal vendors\, and help celebrate one year of Frenzy Coffee! \nDate/Time: F
 riday\, April 3\, 2026 | 10:00 AM – 5:30 PM \nLocation: Frenzy Coffee\, 
 305 1st Street\, Downtown Davis
LOCATION:Frenzy Coffee\, 305 1st St.\, Davis\, CA\, 95616\, United States
URL:https://davisdowntown.com/event/frenzy-coffee-1st-birthday-celebration
 -live-dj-vendors/
X-SOURCE:Davis Downtown
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Day in Downtown – Vendor Market & Street Celebration (Free!)
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260405T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260405T160000
UID:10000496-1775383200-1775404800@davisdowntown.com
DESCRIPTION:Spend a full day exploring Day in Downtown – a vibrant\, fre
 e street event bringing together local talent and community! From 10 AM to
  4 PM\, browse a diverse lineup of vendors on E Street (between 3rd & 4th 
 St.)\, including: \n\nVintage clothing & unique finds\nLocal artists\, mak
 ers\, and creators\nDavis brick-and-mortar shops\nNon-profits sharing thei
 r work\nSpecial spots like Sophia’s Thai Kitchen for tasty bites\n\nDisc
 over one-of-a-kind items\, support small businesses and local organization
 s\, and enjoy the lively energy of downtown Davis. Perfect for a relaxed S
 unday outing with friends\, family\, or solo shopping. Bring reusable bags
  and comfy shoes!
LOCATION:CA
URL:https://davisdowntown.com/event/day-in-downtown-vendor-market-street-c
 elebration-free/
X-SOURCE:Davis Downtown
END:VEVENT
