BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Downtown at Dusk
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260409
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260410
UID:10000072-1775721600-1775754000@davisdowntown.com
DESCRIPTION:Mark your calendars for Downtown at Dusk\, a brand-new event s
 eries bringing together music\, art\, and community right in the heart of 
 the city. Enjoy live performances\, exclusive deals from local businesses\
 , and a chance to celebrate everything that makes Downtown Davis so vibran
 t. \nFounded in 2023\, DRC Creatives is proud to partner with @davis.downt
 own\, @downtownatdusk\, and @citydavisca to make this series possible and 
 give back to the community through music\, art\, and culture. \nTEXT “DO
 WNTOWN” TO\nG ST. (530) 298-8714
LOCATION:CA
URL:https://davisdowntown.com/event/downtown-at-dusk/2026-04-09/
X-SOURCE:Davis Downtown
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Davis Downtown Board Meeting
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260409T090000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260409T100000
UID:10000014-1775725200-1775728800@davisdowntown.com
DESCRIPTION:Join us on the second Thursday of each month for our Governing
  Board of Directors meeting. The meeting is open to all interested. Stay u
 p-to-date on business and initiatives related to downtown Davis\, and the 
 opportunity to provide public comment will be available. \nMeetings are cu
 rrently held virtually on the Zoom platform from 9:00am to 10:00am. If you
  are interested in attending\, please contact us at info@davisdowntown.com
  to request a Zoom meeting invitation. \nTo view\, download and/or print B
 oard of Directors meeting agendas or minutes\, click on the following link
 : https://davisdowntown.com/agendas-meeting-information. \nMeeting locatio
 ns and times are subject to change.
LOCATION:Davis Downtown Board Meeting\, Zoom\, Davis\, CA
URL:https://davisdowntown.com/event/davis-downtown-board-meeting/2026-04-0
 9/
X-SOURCE:Davis Downtown
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:2nd Friday ArtAbout – Monthly Downtown Davis Art Walk & Receptio
 ns (Free!)
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260410T170000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260410T210000
UID:10000170-1775840400-1775854800@davisdowntown.com
DESCRIPTION:Join Davis’s beloved 2nd Friday ArtAbout – a free monthly 
 self-guided artwalk coordinated by the Pence Gallery! Every second Friday\
 , stroll downtown Davis to discover fresh exhibits\, opening receptions\, 
 live music\, hands-on activities\, and direct chats with local and regiona
 l artists at 10+ galleries\, co-ops\, and businesses. \nSupport our vibran
 t arts scene\, uncover unique talent and styles\, and soak up the lively e
 nergy – ideal for friends\, families\, dates\, or solo adventures. Many 
 venues offer complimentary refreshments like wine and snacks. \nFree – n
 o tickets required! \n\nRuns approximately 5:00–9:00 PM (venue reception
 s vary—check the monthly guide for specifics).\nGrab the printed guide (
 with map & details) the week of at the Pence Gallery or participating spot
 s\, or download it at pencegallery.org/events/artabout/.\n\nInterested in 
 hosting as a venue\, artist\, or business? Visit https://pencegallery.org/
 events/artabout/ to fill out the corresponding forms. Please submit event
 s 3 weeks in advance via the form on the site to be included in the guide 
 and promotions. \nStay in the loop: facebook.com/davisartabout \nCome cele
 brate local creativity downtown – see you on the next second Friday! 
 🎨✨
LOCATION:CA
URL:https://davisdowntown.com/event/2nd-friday-artabout/2026-04-10/
X-SOURCE:Davis Downtown
END:VEVENT
